Carl Harbaugh https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carl_Harbaugh 0 Carl Harbaugh (November 10, 1886 – February 26, 1960) was an American film actor, screenwriter and director. He appeared in 59 films between 1912 and 1957. He wrote for a further 46 films and directed 25. He was born in Washington, D.C., and died in Hollywood, California.
